    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193670/extras/41bf04708224a0b4ee613362a1e34b76.avif?t=1747987628\" width=540 height=308 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《对不起！我把美女包围了》是一款模拟恋爱的全动态真人互动影像游戏。作为主角的你 – 陈墨，正是年轻有为、事业起步的阶段，却遭遇了坎坷的事业瓶颈和随之而来的情感纠葛。你将会遇到性格各异的不同美少女，与她们一起去探究故事背后隐藏的真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >QQ群：912619095    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >~~~欢迎大家加入我们的社群~~~粉丝群活动持续中~~~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可甜可辣的双面少女：周柳柳</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193670/extras/2e3b5099b0971893dea78df1d99311ca.poster.avif?t=1747987628\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193670/extras/2e3b5099b0971893dea78df1d99311ca.webm?t=1747987628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193670/extras/2e3b5099b0971893dea78df1d99311ca.mp4?t=1747987628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >青梅竹马的大律师：沈若</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193670/extras/7df10f871330025008ec48a15f10d1bf.poster.avif?t=1747987628\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193670/extras/7df10f871330025008ec48a15f10d1bf.webm?t=1747987628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193670/extras/7df10f871330025008ec48a15f10d1bf.mp4?t=1747987628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >形于言色的隐退偶像：李允儿</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193670/extras/d2dc6bee0cb8e5f9433e6180aeb64b1b.poster.avif?t=1747987628\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193670/extras/d2dc6bee0cb8e5f9433e6180aeb64b1b.webm?t=1747987628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193670/extras/d2dc6bee0cb8e5f9433e6180aeb64b1b.mp4?t=1747987628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >温柔体贴的小帮手：杨洁</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193670/extras/c71b88e3c2682a0abd1ca6fb5ca01073.poster.avif?t=1747987628\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193670/extras/c71b88e3c2682a0abd1ca6fb5ca01073.webm?t=1747987628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193670/extras/c71b88e3c2682a0abd1ca6fb5ca01073.mp4?t=1747987628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >浪漫感性的女强人：孟有容</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193670/extras/6169f037ccac74d64bd3afed72b9800c.poster.avif?t=1747987628\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193670/extras/6169f037ccac74d64bd3afed72b9800c.webm?t=1747987628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193670/extras/6169f037ccac74d64bd3afed72b9800c.mp4?t=1747987628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>产品特色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>沉浸体验</strong> – 全程采用第一人称视角拍摄，沉浸式的场景互动和真人模拟，更贴近的镜头感，带来更沉浸的游戏体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>剧情充实</strong> – 通过不同的角色的分支故事，与主线穿插结合，演绎了流畅、丰富的故事剧情，随着故事深入，才能了解到最后的真结局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>更多互动</strong> – 总共包含30多个结局，80多个分支，除此之外，还有诸多不同类型的QTE小挑战，带来更多的游戏互动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>其他</strong> - 彩蛋故事，隐藏成就，美女写真，更多内容等你发掘。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >感谢先行者同行们做出的努力，让游戏行业又产生新的制作方向。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >新的游戏类型会带来新的机遇和挑战，在制作过程中我们也遇到了不少问题并给予了解决。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大家在游戏过程如果有任何建议或意见，希望也能与我们联系。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >QQ群：912619095</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
